#

Arugula and Beet Salad

40 min
$12
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

NutsDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuickEasy

Description

A refreshing salad that combines the earthy sweetness of beets with the peppery bite of arugula, topped with a zesty dressing.

Ingredients

  • arugula: 4 cups
  • beets (cooked and sliced): 2 medium
  • feta cheese (crumbled): 1/2 cup
  • walnuts (chopped): 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
